There have been no material changes to our critical accounting estimates during the three months ended March 31, 2024. For information regarding our critical accounting estimates, see Item 7. "Management's Discussion and Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations" of our Annual Report on Form 10-K for the year ended December 31, 2023.","textTemplate":"","metadataSeparator":"
","type":"TEXT"}

